{"tid":1919633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反了？ 習近平訪武漢  央視罕見「墓碑」式配圖","createTime":"2020-03-11T02:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T16:31:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07b5ae2d3819face15b7566c6961a641bda86f2a","tid":1919633,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/03/15e026a628267e342dda4d8ed1a57f76-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F15e026a628267e342dda4d8ed1a57f76-800x450.jpg&h=ef7b8c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n習近平10日首次抵達肺炎疫區武漢考察，再次掀起罕見的輿論風波。中共央視、新華網等主要喉舌新聞的配圖，竟然是一個高大的「墓碑」，正中間寫道：「習近平抵達武漢」7個大字。<br />\n<br />\n據中共黨媒報導，習近平乘坐飛機於10日上午抵達武漢市，探望和慰問在前線的醫護人員、中共軍隊、社區工作者、公安、幹部，以及患者和社區居民。<br />\n<br />\n不少細心的網友發現，中共喉舌媒體新華網的相關報導，是一塊高大的「墓碑」，正中間寫道：「習近平來到武漢」7個大字。有意思的是，在這7個字下面，還有一個似香爐一樣的黃鶴樓的圖片。再度引發網友聯想，認為這是想讓領導人「駕鶴西去」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/03/8fd9d0afdd0f44162ab0b71add31c42a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F8fd9d0afdd0f44162ab0b71add31c42a.jpg&h=e343a1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與此同時，中共央視新聞的第一條報導的配圖，最初竟然是一個黑色「墓碑」，時隔不久又換成了藍色。正中間寫道：「習近平抵達武漢」7個大字。<br />\n<br />\n截圖顯示，中午11點16分，央視微博發布的第一條報導的配圖，是黑色「墓碑」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，網友紛紛留言說：<br />\n「這色配，真的晦氣。」<br />\n「確實像一塊墓碑。」<br />\n「感覺是故意的呢，這是要反了！」<br />\n「沒錯，這就是一塊高級黑墓碑。連央視也受不了啦！」<br />\n<br />\n另有推特網友發貼說，央視第一條報導的配圖，加上習近平在武漢視察大批群眾演員肉身築牆保護習的視頻，看上去就像捧着靈位送葬的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    <em>央視第一條報導的配圖，加上這視頻，看着像捧着靈位送葬的隊伍。 <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/dT1SmJqYe0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FdT1SmJqYe0&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=0282c69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/dT1SmJqYe0</a><br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; 多疑的多馬有信心/Disbelieving Faithful (@thomaskuang) March 10, 2020<br />\n</em><br />\n有網友提醒說，央視新聞已經重新排版過了！截圖顯示，中午11點55分，央視微博的圖片已經重新編輯，底色變為黑藍色，字體位置也變了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/03/2-22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F2-22.jpg&h=dc820118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/03/10/a102796247.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F03%2F10%2Fa102796247.html&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=685d085f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/03/10/a102796247.html</a>"},{"pid":"2d468908702e41940800eb95ba9764303a340f37","tid":1919633,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"死人藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4170cf6c30ddba05f704ed46b06956596f13ae2","tid":1919633,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phplNKKfX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phplNKKfX.jpg&h=0eaca8e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"721adace259a62a763c1fb449932633ff127ad58","tid":1919633,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}